    PARRY                 | 1
    POWER_ATTACK          | 2
    IMPROVED_POWER_ATTACK | 3
    COUNTERSPELL          | 4
    FLURRY_OF_BLOWS       | 5
    RAPID_SHOT            | 6
    EXPERTISE             | 7
    IMPROVED_EXPERTISE    | 8
    DEFENSIVE_CASTING     | 9
    DIRTY_FIGHTING        | 10
    DEFENSIVE_STANCE      | 11

    @note Requires @ref combatmodes "NWNX_CombatModes" plugin to work.

